                        Shopper is a beautiful, simple and flexible e-commerce template built on top of Bootstrap. 
                        It includes dozens of components and pages you can use “as is” or customize to build exactly what you need.
                    a(class="btn btn-danger border-none" href="#pages" data-toggle="smooth-scroll").
                        Find Out More
